Data Access Statement

- Ownership: The dataset is provided by the UCI Machine Learning Repository.
- Licensing: The data is publicly available for research and educational purposes. Users are free to use and redistribute the data, provided that proper credit is given to the original source.

Accessing the Data:
- Visit the UCI Machine Learning Repository at Heart Disease Dataset.
- Review the description and metadata associated with the dataset.
- Agree to the terms of use specified by the UCI Machine Learning Repository.
- Download the dataset in the desired format.

Citation
- When using the data, please cite the source as follows:
Dua, D. and Graff, C. (2019). UCI Machine Learning Repository [http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml]. Irvine, CA: University of California, School of Information and Computer Science.

For any questions or further information regarding the dataset, please visit the UCI Machine Learning Repository's contact page.
